%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': {'primaryColor': '#4A90D9', 'primaryTextColor': '#fff', 'primaryBorderColor': '#2C5F8A', 'lineColor': '#333', 'secondaryColor': '#F5A623', 'tertiaryColor': '#7ED321'}}}%%
flowchart TD
    A[Customer subscribes\nto plan] --> B[Initial payment\nauthorized & captured]
    B --> C[Payment method tokenized\n🔒 stored securely in vault]
    C --> D[Subscription created\nStatus: Active]
    D --> E[Next billing date set\nbased on cycle - monthly/annual]

    E --> F[⏰ Billing cycle triggers\non scheduled date]
    F --> G[Retrieve stored payment\ntoken from vault]
    G --> H[Create charge using\nstored token]

    H --> I{Charge result}
    I -->|✅ Success| J[Payment confirmed]
    J --> K[Invoice generated\nReceipt emailed]
    K --> L[Subscription renewed\nNext cycle date set]
    L --> F

    I -->|❌ Failure| M[Classify decline reason]
    M --> N{Decline type}
    N -->|Soft decline\nInsufficient funds| O[Schedule smart retry]
    N -->|Hard decline\nCard expired / cancelled| P[Send card update email]
    N -->|Fraud / Do not honor| Q[Flag for review]

    O --> R{Retry schedule}
    R -->|Day 0| S[First attempt failed]
    S -->|Day 3| T[Retry attempt 2]
    T -->|Day 5| U[Retry attempt 3]
    U -->|Day 7| V[Final retry attempt 4]

    P --> W[Customer updates\npayment method?]
    W -->|Yes| X[Retry with new\npayment method]
    X --> I
    W -->|No after 7 days| V

    T --> TA{Success?}
    TA -->|Yes| J
    TA -->|No| U

    U --> UA{Success?}
    UA -->|Yes| J
    UA -->|No| V

    V --> VA{Final attempt success?}
    VA -->|Yes| J
    VA -->|No| Y[All retries exhausted]

    subgraph DUNNING [📧 Dunning Email Sequence]
        direction TD
        D1[Day 0: Payment failed\nPlease update card] --> D2[Day 3: Second notice\nService may be interrupted]
        D2 --> D3[Day 5: Urgent notice\nAccess will be suspended]
        D3 --> D4[Day 7: Final notice\nSubscription will be cancelled]
    end

    S --> D1
    T --> D2
    U --> D3
    V --> D4

    Y --> Z[Enter grace period\n⚠️ Access may be restricted]
    Z --> AA{Customer action\nduring grace period?}
    AA -->|Updates payment| X
    AA -->|No action| AB[Grace period expires]
    AB --> AC[❌ Subscription cancelled\nInvoluntary churn]

    subgraph PRORATION [Proration on Plan Changes]
        direction TD
        PR1[Customer upgrades\nmid-cycle] --> PR2[Calculate unused time\non current plan]
        PR2 --> PR3[Credit unused portion]
        PR3 --> PR4[Charge prorated amount\nfor new plan]
        PR4 --> PR5[Reset billing cycle\nor keep anchor date]
    end

    style A fill:#4A90D9,color:#fff
    style J fill:#7ED321,color:#fff
    style AC fill:#D0021B,color:#fff
    style Z fill:#F5A623,color:#fff
    style S fill:#D0021B,color:#fff
    style D fill:#7ED321,color:#fff
